\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過多幾年到支那嗰班讀書，唔整爛啲嘢都叫比面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返過鋪頭工就知d野成日俾d小朋友搞爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支蝻兩害成日蝦蝦霸霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad204a44a0052b9eae02692b92cef2edd620028","tid":442261,"uid":35420,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得幾年前有個新聞係張圖係日本公園好多垃圾<br />\n之後啲人撞晒車話係遊客整嘅<br />\n點知俾人回覆踢爆話個公園唔係旅遊區，而日本嘅新聞同網民都話係日本嘅後生仔做，話係日本之恥之類</blockquote><br />\nSo?  一有人讚日本就 一定有某種人衝出黎話日本人點點點<br />\n<br />\n好在你有少少新意唔係講二戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8fd233d2b484cd09da55d385b33565f6e14784","tid":442261,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/205923_35a956c365fa8d88d2120fed00f2f882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F205923_35a956c365fa8d88d2120fed00f2f882.jpg&h=858673cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/205925_05eb56b266f35f6d084e74cb3f615d80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F205925_05eb56b266f35f6d084e74cb3f615d80.jpg&h=dddfa879&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13715c654daba3b8563fe8175af422cac591934e","tid":442261,"uid":1349,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"自編自導自演<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor